quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  54,7,"ja'asɓe ndaarɗe, hiɓe njaltira e genaale ɗeen wano kanuuji caratooɗi."
  54,8,"heñaniiɓe noddoowo on. He'eferɓe ɓeen mbi'a: "Ndee ko ñalaande saɗtunde"."
  54,9,"Ado maɓɓe, yimɓe nuuhu ɓeen yedduno. Ɓe njedfi jiyaaɗo Amen on, ɓe wi'i : "Ko jinnaaɗo!", o kammbanaa."
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, won'de : "Miin on ko mi poolaaɗo, faabo [kam]"."
  54,11,"Min ngudditiri dammbuɗe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam,"
  54,12,"Min puccitiri leydi ndin ɓulli. Ndiye ɗern fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde."
  54,13,"Min ndoondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peŋe,"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka amen. Ɗuum ko njoɓdi [Nuuhu] jeddanooɗo oon."
  54,15,"Gooŋɗii Min ngaccirii [kon ko Min mbaɗi ɓe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi baajitorayɗo?"
  54,16,"Tesko ko hono lepte Am e jeertingol (am) wa'anoo?"
  54,17,"Gooŋɗii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorɗo?"
  54,18,"Aadi'en njedduno. Taskee ko hono lepte am e jeertingol (sm) wa'anoo?"
  54,19,"Min ngurtu e maɓɓe henndu saɗtundu, e ñalaande hiitaande, duumiinde;"
  54,20,"hindu bippitira yimɓe ɓeen, wa si tawii ko ɓe daƴƴe tamaro irtaaɗe."
  54,21,"Taskee ko hono lepte am ɗen e jertingol (am) ngol wa'anoo?"
  54,22,"Gooŋɗii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorɗo?"
  54,23,"Samuuda'en njedduno waajo ngo,"
  54,24,"ɓe mb'i: "Kere ko neɗɗo gooto e amen woni ko min njokkata? Haray min ngonii on tumba e nderr majjere e tamperere."
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jaŋtoore nden wernaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko penoowo nii, townitiiɗo"."
  54,26,"Aray ɓe ngaannda (Ñalnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni penoowo toownitiiɗo on."
  54,27,"Ko Min wurtirooɓe ngelooba ndewa ba ngam, jarribagol ɓe. Aynitu ɓe, muññoɗaa."